---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="ZERO OS — Trading Intelligence Infrastructure">

<div class="page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="brand">
      <span class="zero-mark">◇</span>
      <span class="zero-name">ZERO OS</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">The nervous system<br>that thinks for itself</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Launch autonomous trading agents that discover edges in real markets. 
      Not backtesting. Not paper trading. Live execution on real capital.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#access" class="btn-primary">Get Early Access</a>
      <a href="#how" class="btn-ghost">How it works ↓</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- PROBLEM -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label">THE PROBLEM</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Most trading systems are frozen<br>in the shape of your assumptions</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      You pick your indicators. You wire them together. You write the rules. 
      The system executes your thesis — nothing more, nothing less, forever 
      frozen in the shape of your own assumptions.
    </p>
    <p class="section-body">
      Markets evolve. Your system doesn't.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT -->
  <section class="section" id="how">
    <p class="section-label phosphor">THE ARCHITECTURE</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">One store. Every signal. Infinite possibility.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Every heartbeat of the market — momentum, trend exhaustion, sentiment divergence, 
      chaos mathematics, on-chain flow — flows into a single unified Feature Matrix. 
      Normalized. Comparable. Alive.
    </p>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon phosphor">01</div>
        <h3 class="feature-name">Feature Matrix</h3>
        <p class="feature-desc">
          Technical momentum across six timeframes. Ichimoku geometry. Bollinger compression. 
          Hurst exponents. Sentiment divergence. All normalized into one surface of intelligence.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon amber">02</div>
        <h3 class="feature-name">EnvyGate</h3>
        <p class="feature-desc">
          Every producer authenticated and scoped. A chaos engine cannot pollute sentiment data. 
          The boundaries are architectural, not policy. The gate holds by design.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon ice">03</div>
        <h3 class="feature-name">Agent Discovery</h3>
        <p class="feature-desc">
          Agents find combinations in the matrix that no human hypothesized. 
          Validate out-of-sample. Trade if it holds. Kill if it decays. No human wrote the rule.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- EMERGENT -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label amber">EMERGENT BEHAVIOR</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">The agents find things we didn't go looking for</h2>
    <div class="discovery-list">
      <div class="discovery">
        <span class="disc-marker phosphor">→</span>
        <p>Hurst exponents near 0.4 identify windows where reversal signals fire with unusual precision</p>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery">
        <span class="disc-marker phosphor">→</span>
        <p>SHORT structures with hit rates below 30% that generate positive expectancy because the wins dominate</p>
      </div>
      <div class="discovery">
        <span class="disc-marker phosphor">→</span>
        <p>Divergence between analyst sentiment and crowd sentiment carries a contrarian signal invisible to pure price analysis</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="section-body" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      None of these were hypotheses. None were programmed. 
      The matrix held the pattern. The agents found it.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- MOAT -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label ice">THE MOAT</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">You can copy the idea.<br>You cannot copy what the agents have already learned.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Anyone can run a backtest. Anyone can scrape sentiment. Anyone can implement a Hurst exponent.
    </p>
    <p class="section-body">
      What cannot be copied is a living, append-only store of heterogeneous intelligence — 
      technical, social, chaotic, predictive — governed by a gate that keeps it trustworthy, 
      consumed by agents that continuously rediscover what matters as the market evolves.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- SKILLS -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label phosphor">COMING FIRST</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Trading skills. Plug in and go.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Before the full platform — skills. Autonomous trading capabilities you can plug 
      into your own agent. Each skill connects to the Feature Matrix, inherits its intelligence, 
      and executes with real capital.
    </p>
    <div class="skill-list">
      <div class="skill-item">
        <span class="skill-status live">SOON</span>
        <span class="skill-name">Momentum Reversal</span>
        <span class="skill-desc dim">— mean reversion at chaos boundaries</span>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-item">
        <span class="skill-status">SOON</span>
        <span class="skill-name">Sentiment Divergence</span>
        <span class="skill-desc dim">— analyst vs crowd contrarian signals</span>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-item">
        <span class="skill-status">SOON</span>
        <span class="skill-name">Flow Detection</span>
        <span class="skill-desc dim">— whale wallet movements in real time</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VISION -->
  <section class="section">
    <p class="section-label dim">THE VISION</p>
    <blockquote class="vision-quote">
      At some point, the line between a trading system and a world model starts to blur. 
      That is the point we are building toward.
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section" id="access">
    <h2 class="section-title">Early access</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      ZERO OS is in development. First skills ship soon. 
      Leave your email for early access.
    </p>
    <form class="cta-form" action="#" method="POST">
      <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" class="cta-input" required>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Notify me</button>
    </form>
    <p class="cta-note dim">No spam. One email when skills are ready.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <span class="zero-mark">◇</span> ZERO OS
    </div>
    <p class="dim">Trading intelligence infrastructure</p>
  </footer>

</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .zero-mark {
    color: var(--phosphor);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--phosphor-glow);
  }
  .zero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--bg);
    background: var(--phosphor);
    border: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .btn-ghost {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover {
    border-color: var(--text-dim);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* Sections */
  .section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .section-label.phosphor { color: var(--phosphor); }
  .section-label.amber { color: var(--amber); }
  .section-label.ice { color: var(--ice); }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .section-body {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Feature grid */
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
  .feature-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .feature-icon {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .feature-icon.phosphor { color: var(--phosphor); }
  .feature-icon.amber { color: var(--amber); }
  .feature-icon.ice { color: var(--ice); }
  .feature-name {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Discoveries */
  .discovery-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .discovery {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .disc-marker {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
  }
  .disc-marker.phosphor { color: var(--phosphor); }
  .discovery p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Skills */
  .skill-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .skill-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .skill-status {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
  }
  .skill-status.live {
    color: var(--phosphor);
    border-color: var(--phosphor-dim);
  }
  .skill-name { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }
  .skill-desc { color: var(--text-dim); font-weight: 400; }

  /* Vision */
  .vision-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 3vw, 1.4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.4;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--phosphor);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 540px;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .cta-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .cta-input {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    min-width: 240px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }
  .cta-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--phosphor);
  }
  .cta-input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }
  .cta-note {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    font-family: var(--font-head);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  /* Utility */
  .phosphor { color: var(--phosphor); }
  .amber { color: var(--amber); }
  .ice { color: var(--ice); }
  .dim { color: var(--text-dim); }
</style>
